source:
TEXT_LUCKZH202_03530_SEQ_00<tab><var 48 F201FC /var><var 49 F201FD /var> Quest Sync<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>
The Talos enthusiast seems to recognize you from somewhere.
target:
TEXT_LUCKZH202_03530_SEQ_00<tab><var 48 F201FC /var><var 49 F201FD /var> Schwierigkeitsanpassung<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>
Ein begeisterter Talosarbeiter scheint emsig mit dem Sammeln eines Materials beschäftigt zu sein, aus dem Taloi bestehen.

source: TEXT_LUCKZH202_03530_TODO_00<tab>Use the steel lever to remove core housing components from the abandoned Talos.
target: TEXT_LUCKZH202_03530_TODO_00<tab><var 2B ((<var 32 ((EventItem)) 03F61E8F32020502 /var>)) /var> an <var 32 ((EObj)) 06F61EAD12030402 /var> verwenden, um Talosziegel zu erhalten

source: TEXT_LUCKZH202_03530_TODO_01<tab>Deliver the core housing components to the Talos enthusiast.
target: TEXT_LUCKZH202_03530_TODO_01<tab>Dem begeisterten Talosarbeiter die Talosziegel geben

source: TEXT_LUCKZH202_03530_MINER03530_00O_000<tab>I know you! You're one of the people who raised that enormous Talos!
target: TEXT_LUCKZH202_03530_MINER03530_00O_000<tab>Bist du <var 08 E905 ((die)) ((der)) /var> Reisende, <var 08 E905 ((die)) ((der)) /var> die Taloi wieder in Bewegung gesetzt hat? Wärst du bereit, mir bei etwas zu helfen?

source: TEXT_LUCKZH202_03530_MINER03530_00O_001<tab>It was a day I'll never forget. To think that inside it was the core that Agna unearthed... It brought tears to my eyes.
target: TEXT_LUCKZH202_03530_MINER03530_00O_001<tab>Dank dir haben in Pfotenschlag viele wieder damit angefangen, Taloi für Arbeiten einzusetzen.

source: TEXT_LUCKZH202_03530_MINER03530_00O_002<tab>And I wasn't alone. We were all reminded that she gave her life trying to bring Talos back to Amh Araeng. Many of us, myself included, wish to continue her work. Even without the Daedalus Stoneworks, we'll find a way.
target: TEXT_LUCKZH202_03530_MINER03530_00O_002<tab>Von dem, was Magnus' Frau vollbracht hat, sollen auch weiterhin alle profitieren!

source: TEXT_LUCKZH202_03530_MINER03530_00O_003<tab>Of course, there is a lot more to Talos than their cores. The parts that house them are equally important. We're collecting them for use in our tests, with the aim of eventually building our own from scratch.
target: TEXT_LUCKZH202_03530_MINER03530_00O_003<tab>Aus diesem Grund habe ich die zurückgekehrten Taloi untersucht. Ihr Herz, also ihr Antriebskern, braucht anscheinend eine Art Verstärkung. Um daran zu arbeiten, sammle ich Talosziegel.

source: TEXT_LUCKZH202_03530_MINER03530_00O_004<tab>Perhaps you could lend us a hand, if you're not too busy. With these old Stoneworks tools, you should be able to open one up and take out the housing components inside. We'd be grateful for anything you can bring us!
target: TEXT_LUCKZH202_03530_MINER03530_00O_004<tab>Du wärst mir eine große Hilfe, wenn du hier am Nassen Bahnhof von <var 32 ((EObj)) 06F61EAD12030402 /var> diese Ziegel für mich besorgen könntest. Verwende dazu bitte <var 32 ((EventItem)) 07F61E8F32020502 /var>.

source: TEXT_LUCKZH202_03530_MINER03530_00O_010<tab>The Daedalus Stoneworks did a remarkable job of building their Talos. Even now, years after they were abandoned, they're a bugger to take apart without the right tools.
target: TEXT_LUCKZH202_03530_MINER03530_00O_010<tab>Verwende bitte <var 32 ((EventItem)) 03F61E8F32020502 /var>, um mir Talosziegel von <var 32 ((EObj)) 06F61EAD12030402 /var> zu besorgen.

source: TEXT_LUCKZH202_03530_MINER03530_00O_021<tab>Ho ho! You don't see many like these! And this one shows almost no signs of wear and tear at all. I can't wait to show the others!
target: TEXT_LUCKZH202_03530_MINER03530_00O_021<tab>Oho, du hast drei Stück gesammelt und einer davon ist sogar unbeschädigt!

source: TEXT_LUCKZH202_03530_MINER03530_00O_022<tab>Of course, we still have a long way to go before we can build our very own Talos, but you've been an enormous help. Many thanks!
target: TEXT_LUCKZH202_03530_MINER03530_00O_022<tab>Damit kann ich weiter daran arbeiten, den Antriebskern zu verstärken. Ich danke dir, <var 08 E905 ((Reisende)) ((Reisender)) /var>.
